title: The Gavin McInnes Show 2016-02-01 Episode 86 Luis J. Gomez

The always outspoken and "controversial" Gavin McInnes joins the Anthony Cumia Network - with new shows twice a week. In addition to co-founding VICE, the author, actor, podcast host, and political pundit is at the forefront of the modern "anti-PC" movement and a perfect match for the cutting edge and newly emerging ACN.

Guests: Luis J. Gomez, Allison Klemp, Jim Goad

Episode 86: Today on TGMS, Gavin talks about his Jada Pinkett Smith controversy, Luis J. Gomez talks about Gavin's set at The Stand, Allison Klemp talks about some of her experiences, and Jim Goad talks about assault statistics.
